KELLER WILLIAMS REALTY AT THE PARKS

data.description: The single story home is located in Shingle Creek Reserve at the Oaks. With just under 1700 sf of heated living space, your split floorplan home has 3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms. The living, dining room and Gourmet Kitchen share a large space off the entryway.  The Gourmet style kitchen offers an abundance of counter space, natural light, dark appliances and closet pantry. It features course countertops and a spacious island that serves as the heart of the home. This community includes a host of activities to keep the entire family busy including a golfing, parks, basketball court, tennis court, lake access for boating, a nature trail for taking in the local wildlife and a boardwalk sitting area to watch the sun go down over the large pond. Shingle Creek is a short drive to The Loop offering outdoor shopping, dining, and entertainment.Schedule a day to the beach with just an hour drive away. Call now to schedule your private viewing today!
